SELECT			E.*, 
				CONCAT(E.ExpenseTitle, '') AS ExpenseLookupCaption, 
				E.MemoTitle,
				'' AS _Other

 WHERE 1 = 1  ORDER BY ExpenseTitle ASC  LIMIT 0, 200
